{"tid":2246252,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"芬蘭暫停與香港引渡協議　中方強烈不滿和堅決反對","createTime":"2020-10-17T01:52:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T05:52:54.000Z","uid":230530,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0d0cc3292f48710f7406ad9ecb1d02acabe45097","tid":2246252,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:52:10.000Z","msg":"芬蘭決定因應港區國安法，正式暫停同香港的引渡協議。芬蘭政府的公報指，總統尼尼斯特批准司法部的相關建議。芬蘭外長在港區國安法七月生效時指，香港情況出現變化，認為同香港的引渡協議不再適用。<br />\n<br />\n由美國、英國、加拿大、澳洲及新西蘭組成的五眼聯盟，以及法國和德國已先後暫停同香港的引渡協議。 中方對芬蘭暫停與香港的引渡協議，表達強烈不滿和堅決反對，敦促芬蘭恪守國際法和國際關係基本準則，停止以任何方式干涉香港事務和中國內政，以免損害中芬關係大局。 <br />\n<br />\n中國駐芬蘭使館發言人表示，港區國安法是確保「一國兩制」行穩致遠的重要舉措，有助香港法律體系更完備、社會秩序更穩定、營商環境更良好，有利香港長治久安和長期繁榮穩定，強調香港事務純屬中國內政，不容外部勢力干預，  <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2361999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2361999&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao3vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=e49d0a6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2361999</a>"},{"pid":"25cc543fd19f8379c34694bb783f8f3cb3db25ea","tid":2246252,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:52:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c766ea8cd4ce8c89a88dc5d68aec556ffc2be88","tid":2246252,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:53:01.000Z","msg":"Nokia復興<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45eff1bc8818239c1455f4fe51f06c0fe0cc7ab","tid":2246252,"uid":155095,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:53:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/XI_mand.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2FXinwen%2FXI_mand.jpg&h=51c9f3cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg5-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/118586009_2696433937271345_5128324791330